7824D7F"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "2560x1440-RD (1).png", "id": "547191818112728", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035448_547191821446061_8962058648831132714_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=83lIJ7GBaDgQ7kNvgGEWtyv&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDn25QoP86nD9vEP2h3Myb3CyVOsZx6FlnVCCxDntks5A&oe=678266E1"}, "display_name": "Track Craft", "keywords": ["track", "craft", "racing", "car", "mixed"], "long_description": "**Track Craft is a mixed-reality racing game where you can turn your surroundings into a racetrack.**\n\n\n# ULTIMATE MR PLAYGROUND \n\nUse your surroundings and turn them into a mixed-reality race track.\n\n{1272215014134973}\n\n\n# EXPLORE DIFFERENT WORLDS\n\nGet behind the wheel and experience the 104 pre-built tracks spread across 5 different worlds. Each brings new mechanics, challenges, cars, and skins to unlock.\n\n{2499265100265459}\n\n\n# CRAFT YOUR OWN TRACKS\n\nCreate tracks intuitively thanks to full hand tracking and share them online. Or just race on new tracks created by the community every day.\n\n{1695057567991201}\n\n\n\n# ONLINE MULTIPLAYER\n\nPlay and Craft with your friends at home or online with players across the globe.\n\n{1046525373656002}\n\n\n\n# BUILD UP YOUR COLLECTION\n\nUnlock new exciting cars by collecting stars.\n\n{850050203892697}\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n# THE FUN NEVER ENDS\n\n\n\nAvailable on Quest 3/3s, Quest Pro, and Quest 2.", "short_description": "Track Craft is a mixed-reality racing game where you can turn your surroundings into gravity-defying racetracks. Drive tiny cars, craft exciting tracks, and race daily on new circuits with friends or other players.\n\nCRAFT. SHARE. RACE. REPEAT."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.gamify.cz/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.gamify.cz/terms-of-service", "publisher_name": "Brainz Gamify s.r.o.", "supp